GSD.description:
tracing: kprobe: Fix memory leak in test_gen_kprobe/kretprobe_cmd()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.154 by commit bef08acbe560a926b4cee9cc46404cc98ae5703b, it was introduced in version v5.6 by commit 64836248dda20c8e7427b493f7e06d9bf8f58850. For more details please see the references link.
